{"about_the_game":"You\u00b4ve just been fired from a major supermarket chain..<br><br>Now build your own and show them who\u00b4s the <strong>boss!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/BuildYourMarket.png?t=1729782281\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/BuildYourMarket.gif?t=1729782281\" /><br><br><strong>Organize and build the different structures wherever and however you want.</strong><br><br>You'll have at your disposal various types of structures, such as shelves or workstations, to expand the range of products in your supermarket, such as quality meat, the freshest fish, or a delicious cheesecake.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/ManageYourTimeAndStock.png?t=1729782281\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/ManagerYourStock.gif?t=1729782281\" /><br><br><strong>Manage your time and your product stock daily.</strong><br><br>The day will pass quickly, and you'll need to ensure that your shelves are always full. To do this, manage the warehouse, expand it with each upgrade, and hire employees to automatically stock products during the day.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/HireYourWorkers.png?t=1729782281\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/ManagerYourWorkers.gif?t=1729782281\" /><br><br><strong>Use your manager intelligent and hire the best employees.</strong><br><br>Each employee will be different from the last. You'll need to use your eagle eye to distinguish the best employees for each task, assigning each one a primary and a secondary duty. Oh, and don't forget to pay them their salary!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/SurvivTheWorkday.png?t=1729782281\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/RandomEvents.gif?t=1729782281\" /><br><br><strong>Every day is different in Mercapolis, adapt to each day as if it were the last.</strong><br><br>Various random events will occur during the day, and you'll need to be prepared as a manager to face them. Robberies, fires, or even health inspectors issuing fines if you're not vigilant enough.<br><br><br>Project made for the Espetos Studios in Interactive Product Design degree of U-tad, University of Technology, Arts and Design.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/EspetosLogoSteam.png?t=1729782281\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930040/extras/UtadLogo.png?t=1729782281\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Paco with a Job","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/624d50bd3d928c2615dd44bc9976b1a0f78df605.jpg"},{"name":"King of the Market","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/2dc06b6a934fb26aad6b54516fa57c28de380705.jpg"},{"name":"First Signing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/a5576529b1fd51f5526a600952bfddc97eeaa907.jpg"},{"name":"Worker of the Month!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/290a0a59ef9e63029ac8773758433207be7187fa.jpg"},{"name":"Changes are good","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/cadd417e979d33c0d1838effd8c85a09f2f33ea2.jpg"},{"name":"A Good Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2930040/